<p><strong>Small humanoid (kobold), lawful evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 15 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 27 (5d6+10)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.</p>

